# TC11: ChargeBattery4
# Precondition setup: power ON, LowBatteryMode, battery below threshold
# Action: start charging
# Expected: charging starts and battery increases.
# Current implementation clears LowBatteryMode to StandbyMode after one charge tick if battery > threshold.
power
battery 5
low-battery
expect power on
expect mode LowBatteryMode
expect battery 5
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
charge
expect charging on
expect battery 15
expect mode StandbyMode
expect motor stopped
expect cleaner off
exit
